{"tid":912411,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"近排小腿肌肉好繃緊 點算","createTime":"2018-11-22T15:49:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T17:47:19.000Z","uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4586d14822fff3a5c17c597561f3f47e0b78ecb5","tid":912411,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T15:49:41.000Z","msg":"我一返到屋企就好鍾意瞓喺度玩電話 又成日孿喺梳化度睇電視<br />\n一直都無乜大問題 但去到近排左邊小腿開始肌肉好繃緊 <br />\n去到瞓覺 小腿肌肉都好似跑緊步咁 好辛苦 點擺隻小腿都係繃緊<br />\n點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無d咩方法舒緩／改善到 唔想以後都係咁"},{"pid":"2324707a18eb564bfda150a43909ba6da3feddae","tid":912411,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T16:22:51.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"353870577827bbb1e7d2b02c0b6cba94071f07b6","tid":912411,"uid":161190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T16:31:45.000Z","msg":"咁埋屌鬆佢囉"},{"pid":"f2fb18ae37538f2df0ed67ac02fe641fc07cb7b9","tid":912411,"uid":218169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T16:34:10.000Z","msg":"用力渣舊肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一開頭好緊會好撚痛<br />\n不過一陣就唔痛同埋會鬆哂<br />\n可以試下我有時都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b779939e564115b9faa86b4d2f5a082b3c0b39a","tid":912411,"uid":207977,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T16:35:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sG38PZL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsG38PZL.png&h=af976904&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n先靠牆依個動作拉小腿<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6xrFF6s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6xrFF6s.png&h=811c8826&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後坐低做攀足式，拉埋大腿膕旁肌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n簡單嘅就做以上方法，希望幫到你"},{"pid":"c4e1d3813bce10fa6e1b3a91b19fce6ff283efba","tid":912411,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"353870577827bbb1e7d2b